kchmviewer (4.1-1maemo2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Source is based on 4.1-1, changes have been made before Faheem Pervez's changes
  * debian folder taken from 4.1-1maemo1
  * Some changes to rules file (disable debug, optimize build for N8xO)
